cript><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/turbopack-37655peecauic.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/158myu8e_yme3.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0wm93jxy2eaun.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/3tkferufqdo5j.js\" async=\"\"></script><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/150?img=7\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/150?img=8\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/150?img=9\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/150?img=10\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/150?img=11\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/150?img=12\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/150?img=13\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/150?img=14\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/150?img=15\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/150?img=16\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/150?img=17\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/150?img=18\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/150?img=19\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/150?img=20\"/><meta name=\"next-size-adjust\" content=\"\"/><title>Snab Infotech</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"AI-enabled product development, app development, website development, desktop software, and agent workflow consulting.\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0cz1d0mv5g_q7.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><header class=\"topbar\" aria-label=\"Primary navigation\"><a class=\"brand\" href=\"#\" aria-label=\"Snab Infotech home\"><span class=\"brand-mark\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></span><span class=\"brand-name\">Snab Infotech</span></a><div class=\"mobile-menu-root\"><button class=\"menu-trigger\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Open menu\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"_R_aavb_\"><span class=\"menu-label\">Menu</span><span class=\"menu-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span><span></span></span></button></div></header><div id=\"smooth-wrapper\"><div id=\"smooth-content\"><main class=\"site-shell\"><section class=\"hero\" id=\"home\" aria-labelledby=\"hero-title\"><div class=\"grid-plane\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"scanline\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"hero-copy\"><p class=\"eyebrow\">Your products are now AI-enabled.<br/>Native agent workflows for teams, tools, and operations →</p><h1 id=\"hero-title\">The AI Brain Behind Your Business</h1><p class=\"lead\">AI-enabled apps, websites, desktop software, and workflow agents built from scratch or upgraded from your existing product.</p><div class=\"cta-row\"><a class=\"btn btn-light btn-large\" href=\"/contact\">Talk to us</a></div></div><img class=\"pixel-tree\" src=\"/pixel-tree-wind.svg\" alt=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\"/><div class=\"bottom-rail\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div></section><section class=\"proof-section\" aria-labelledby=\"proof-title\"><div class=\"proof-top-rail\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"company-marquee\" aria-label=\"Companies using Snab\"><div class=\"company-track\"><div class=\"company-tile\"><span class=\"company-logo logo-smallest\">smallest.ai</span></div><div class=\"company-tile\"><span class=\"company-logo logo-neuroform\">neuroform.ai</span></div><div class=\"company-tile\"><span class=\"company-logo logo-syntrix\">SYNTRIX</span></div><div class=\"company-tile\"><span class=\"company-logo logo-composio\">Composio</span></div><div class=\"company-tile\"><span class=\"company-logo logo-calsoft\">calsoft</span></div><div class=\"company-tile\"><span class=\"company-logo logo-smallest\">smallest.ai</span></div><div class=\"company-tile\"><span class=\"company-logo logo-neuroform\">neuroform.ai</span></div><div class=\"company-tile\"><span class=\"company-logo logo-syntrix\">SYNTRIX</span></div><div class=\"company-tile\"><span class=\"company-logo logo-composio\">Composio</span></div><div class=\"company-tile\"><span class=\"company-logo logo-calsoft\">calsoft</span></div><div class=\"company-tile\"><span class=\"company-logo logo-smallest\">smallest.ai</span></div><div class=\"company-tile\"><span class=\"company-logo logo-neuroform\">neuroform.ai</span></div><div class=\"company-tile\"><span class=\"company-logo logo-syntrix\">SYNTRIX</span></div><div class=\"company-tile\"><span class=\"company-logo logo-composio\">Composio</span></div><div class=\"company-tile\"><span class=\"company-logo logo-calsoft\">calsoft</span></div></div></div><div class=\"funding-block\"><h2 id=\"proof-title\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>End-to-End AI Product Partner<span aria-hidden=\"true\"></span></h2><p class=\"funding-line\"><span>Product Strategy</span><span>AI Engineering</span><span>Full-Stack Development</span><span>Workflow Automation</span><span>and more</span></p></div><div class=\"metric-row\" aria-label=\"Performance metrics\"><article class=\"metric-card\"><p class=\"metric-value\">3 PLATFORMS</p><p class=\"metric-label\">Web, Mobile &amp; Desktop</p></article><article class=\"metric-card\"><p class=\"metric-value\">2 PRODUCTS</p><p class=\"metric-label\">Interview Expert &amp; Notary Expert</p></article><article class=\"metric-card\"><p class=\"metric-value\">4 CORE SERVICES</p><p class=\"metric-label\">Build, Integrate, Automate &amp; Consult</p></article><article class=\"metric-card\"><p class=\"metric-value\">1 TEAM</p><p class=\"metric-label\">From Strategy to Production</p></article></div><div class=\"proof-bottom-rail\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div></section><section class=\"services-section\" id=\"services\" aria-labelledby=\"services-title\"><div class=\"services-grid-plane\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"services-header\"><h2 id=\"services-title\">Everything You Need To<br/>Build Intelligent Software</h2></div><div class=\"services-board\"><article class=\"service-card service-product\"><div class=\"service-copy\"><h3>Build New<br/>AI Products</h3><p class=\"service-description\">We take AI products from strategy and UX to engineering and launch.</p><p class=\"service-capability\">STRATEGY  /  UX  /  ENGINEERING</p></div><div class=\"service-asset-slot\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><video class=\"service-asset-media\" src=\"/slot1.mp4\" autoPlay=\"\" muted=\"\" playsInline=\"\"></video></div></article><article class=\"service-card service-integration\"><div class=\"service-copy\"><h3>Make Existing<br/>Software Intelligent</h3><p class=\"service-description\">We add assistants, RAG, search and automation to existing software.</p><p class=\"service-capability\">ASSISTANTS  /  RAG  /  SEARCH</p></div><div class=\"service-asset-slot\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><img class=\"service-asset-media\" src=\"/slot2.svg\" alt=\"\"/></div></article><article class=\"service-card service-automation\"><div class=\"service-copy\"><h3>Automate Work<br/>Across Your Company</h3><p class=\"service-description\">We connect documents, systems and teams into intelligent workflows.</p><p class=\"service-capability\">DOCUMENTS  /  SYSTEMS  /  APPROVALS</p></div><div class=\"service-asset-slot\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><video class=\"service-asset-media\" src=\"/slot%203.mp4\" autoPlay=\"\" loop=\"\" muted=\"\" playsInline=\"\"></video></div></article><article class=\"service-card service-strategy\"><div class=\"service-copy\"><h3>Plan Your<br/>AI Transformation</h3><p class=\"service-description\">We turn AI opportunities into a practical roadmap for production.</p><p class=\"service-capability\">READINESS  /  ARCHITECTURE  /  ROADMAP</p></div><div class=\"service-asset-slot\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><video class=\"service-asset-media\" src=\"/slot4.mp4\" autoPlay=\"\" loop=\"\" muted=\"\" playsInline=\"\"></video></div></article></div><div class=\"bottom-rail\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div></section><section class=\"projects-section\" id=\"projects\" aria-labelledby=\"projects-title\"><div class=\"projects-header\"><h2 id=\"projects-title\">PROJECTS</h2><p class=\"projects-intro\">AI products for real-world professional workflows.</p></div><div class=\"projects-panel\"><a class=\"project-row\" href=\"#\"><span class=\"project-number\">01</span><span class=\"project-name-wrap\"><span class=\"project-name\">Interview Expert</span><span class=\"project-row-underline\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span></span><span class=\"project-categories\"><span>INTERVIEW AUTOMATION</span><span>AI PRODUCT</span><span>WORKFLOW SOFTWARE</span></span><span class=\"project-summary\"><span class=\"project-description\">An AI-enabled platform that helps teams organize interview workflows, reduce administrative work, and turn interview information into structured, actionable records.</span><span class=\"project-capabilities\"><span>Workflow Management<span aria-hidden=\"true\"> · </span></span><span>Interview Assistance<span aria-hidden=\"true\"> · </span></span><span>Summaries<span aria-hidden=\"true\"> · </span></span><span>Evaluation Support</span></span><span class=\"project-link\">VIEW PROJECT ↗</span></span><span class=\"project-media-slot\"><img class=\"project-media-image\" src=\"/interviewxpert.png\" alt=\"Interview Expert mark\"/></span></a><a class=\"project-row\" href=\"#\"><span class=\"project-number\">02</span><span class=\"project-name-wrap\"><span class=\"project-name\">Notary Expert</span><span class=\"project-row-underline\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span></span><span class=\"project-categories\"><span>NOTARY AUTOMATION</span><span>LEGAL WORKFLOWS</span><span>AI PRODUCT</span></span><span class=\"project-summary\"><span class=\"project-description\">An intelligent workflow platform that helps notary professionals manage documents, appointments, client communication, and case progress more efficiently.</span><span class=\"project-capabilities\"><span>Client Intake<span aria-hidden=\"true\"> · </span></span><span>Document Workflows<span aria-hidden=\"true\"> · </span></span><span>Appointment Coordination<span aria-hidden=\"true\"> · </span></span><span>Case Tracking</span></span><span class=\"project-link\">VIEW PROJECT ↗</span></span><span class=\"project-media-slot\"><img class=\"project-media-image\" src=\"/notary-expert.png\" alt=\"Notary Expert seal\"/></span></a></div><div class=\"projects-footer\"><p>Have a workflow that should be more intelligent?</p><a href=\"/contact\">BUILD WITH SNABB AI ↗</a></div><a class=\"projects-view-all\" href=\"#\">View all projects</a><div class=\"bottom-rail\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div></section><section class=\"business-growth-section\" id=\"contact\" aria-labelledby=\"business-growth-title\"><video class=\"growth-tree-video\" src=\"/tree-growing.mp4\" autoPlay=\"\" loop=\"\" muted=\"\" playsInline=\"\"></video><div class=\"business-growth-copy\"><p class=\"business-growth-kicker\">Growth systems for ambitious teams</p><h2 id=\"business-growth-title\">Build The Next Branch Of Your Business With Us.</h2><blockquote>“Grow your business with AI products, automation, and software services that turn one strong idea into many working systems.”</blockquote><a class=\"business-growth-link\" href=\"/contact\">START A PROJECT ↗</a></div><div class=\"bottom-rail\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div></section><section class=\"testimonials-section\" aria-labelledby=\"testimonials-title\"><div class=\"testimonials-header\"><p class=\"testimonials-eyebrow\">Client Feedback</p><h2 id=\"testimonials-title\">What Our Clients<br/>Are Saying</h2><p class=\"testimonials-intro\">Real feedback from teams who transformed their workflows with us.</p></div><div class=\"testimonials-carousel\"><div class=\"relative w-full overflow-hidden bg-muted/30\" style=\"height:420px\"><div class=\"absolute left-1/2 top-1/2 cursor-pointer border-2 p-5 transition-all 