olute bottom-5 left-5 right-5 mt-2 text-xs italic text-muted-foreground\">- <!-- -->Dan, CTO at SecureNet</p></div><div class=\"absolute left-1/2 top-1/2 cursor-pointer border-2 p-5 transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out z-0 bg-card text-card-foreground border-border hover:border-primary/50\" style=\"width:280px;height:238px;clip-path:polygon(30px 0%, calc(100% - 30px) 0%, 100% 30px, 100% 100%, calc(100% - 30px) 100%, 30px 100%, 0 100%, 0 0);transform:translate(-50%, -50%) \n          translateX(-1400px)\n          translateY(-10px)\n          rotate(-2deg);box-shadow:0px 0px 0px 0px transparent\"><span class=\"absolute block origin-top-right rotate-45 bg-border\" style=\"right:-2px;top:28px;width:70.71067811865476px;height:2px\"></span><img src=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/150?img=3\" alt=\"Stephanie\" class=\"mb-3 h-10 w-9 bg-muted object-cover object-top\" style=\"box-shadow:2px 2px 0px hsl(var(--background))\"/><h3 class=\"text-sm sm:text-base font-medium text-foreground\">“<!-- -->I know it&#x27;s cliche, but we were lost before we found COMPANY. Can&#x27;t thank you guys enough!<!-- -->”</h3><p class=\"absolute bottom-5 left-5 right-5 mt-2 text-xs italic text-muted-foreground\">- <!-- -->Stephanie, COO at InnovateCo</p></div><div class=\"absolute left-1/2 top-1/2 cursor-pointer border-2 p-5 transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out z-0 bg-card text-card-foreground border-border hover:border-primary/50\" style=\"width:280px;height:238px;clip-path:polygon(30px 0%, calc(100% - 30px) 0%, 100% 30px, 100% 100%, calc(100% - 30px) 100%, 30px 100%, 0 100%, 0 0);transform:translate(-50%, -50%) \n          translateX(-1225px)\n          translateY(10px)\n          rotate(2deg);box-shadow:0px 0px 0px 0px transparent\"><span class=\"absolute block origin-top-right rotate-45 bg-border\" style=\"right:-2px;top:28px;width:70.71067811865476px;height:2px\"></span><img src=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/150?img=4\" alt=\"Marie\" class=\"mb-3 h-10 w-9 bg-muted object-cover object-top\" style=